		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Wondrous Item - Rare</em></p><p><em>A magic item like this counts as magical for overcoming effects.</em></p><p><strong>Buff</strong></p><ul><li><p>This fine black cloth folds to a handkerchief. Unfolding it creates a 6-foot-diameter opening into a 10-foot-deep extradimensional cylinder. The space is sealed to that plane (no open passages).</p></li><li><p>Creatures inside can climb out while itâ€™s open. Taking an Action to fold the cloth closes the hole; creatures and objects inside remain in the extradimensional space, and the hole weighs next to nothing.</p></li><li><p>While closed, a creature inside can take an Action to make a Athletics Check (DC 10); on a success it forces its way out within 5 feet of the Portable Hole.</p></li><li><p>A closed hole holds enough air for 1 hour of breathing, divided by the number of breathing creatures inside.</p></li><li><p>Placing a Portable Hole inside an extradimensional space (Bag of Holding, Handy Haversack, etc.) destroys both and opens a one-way gate to the Astral Plane. Any creature within 10 feet not behind Total Cover is pulled through to a random Astral location; the gate then closes.</p></li></ul>",
